WEBVTT

00:00:27.963 --> 00:00:31.492
Deyarli hamma vaqti-vaqti bilan 
tushkunlik hissini tuyadi.

00:00:31.492 --> 00:00:32.711
Yomon baho olish,

00:00:32.711 --> 00:00:33.808
ishdan ayrilish,

00:00:33.808 --> 00:00:34.831
urushib qolish,

00:00:34.831 --> 00:00:38.064
hattoki yomg’irli kun ham ma’yus hislarni 
chorlashi mumkin.

00:00:38.064 --> 00:00:39.891
Ba’zida hech qanday sabab bo’lmaydi.

00:00:39.891 --> 00:00:42.006
U to’satdan paydo bo’ladi.

00:00:42.006 --> 00:00:43.549
Vaziyat o’zgarganidan so’ng,

00:00:43.549 --> 00:00:46.206
bu ma'yus tuyg'ular g’oyib bo’ladi.

00:00:46.206 --> 00:00:48.419
Klinik depressiya bundan farq qiladi.

00:00:48.419 --> 00:00:49.896
U tibbiy kasallik hisoblanib,

00:00:49.896 --> 00:00:52.778
istaklaringizga bo’ysunib, 
sizni shunchaki tark etmaydi.

00:00:52.778 --> 00:00:55.180
U kamida ikki haftadan oshiq davom etib,

00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:58.783
kishining ishlash, o’ynash va sevish
qobiliyatiga

00:00:58.783 --> 00:00:59.590
jiddiy

00:00:59.590 --> 00:01:00.996
ta'sir ko'rsatadi.